  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Improvement in Cardiopulmonary Fitness after Ingestion of CS and Lingzhi Extracts</measure>
    <time_frame>28 days</time_frame>
    <description>Before and after 28-day ingestion of CS and Lingzhi extracts, subjects will undergo a graded exercise test on a treadmill and results will be compared.</description>
